Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.65,0:00:08.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}这个国家
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.28,0:00:10.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}财阀举办从古至今传承的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.11,0:00:14.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}从没有被公诸于世的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.95,0:00:18.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}惨绝人寰的赌博比赛
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.39,0:00:38.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}成功
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.97,0:00:40.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}女高中生得手
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.77,0:00:41.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}牛逼
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.98,0:00:44.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}这是中大奖了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.52,0:00:45.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}剥光她 剥光她
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.23,0:00:46.19,Default - up,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}忍不住了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.19,0:00:47.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}太棒了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.48,0:00:49.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}这女的巨乳啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.40,0:00:51.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}大棒了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.15,0:00:54.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}为什么会变成这样 为什么会变成这样…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.15,0:00:54.28,Default - up,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}喂 野本
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.70,0:00:56.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}往秩父方向开
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.41,0:00:59.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}随便玩玩以后就扔了这女的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.20,0:01:01.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}那…那个啊 北条
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.54,0:01:04.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}我听说是去搭讪才跟着你们来的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.25,0:01:05.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}这是犯罪吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.37,0:01:07.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}还是别…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.92,0:01:08.42,Default - up,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}你害怕个鬼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.42,0:01:10.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}你也是共犯啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.46,0:01:11.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}不要
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.55,0:01:13.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}过会儿也让你来一发
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.92,0:01:16.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}反正你肯定是处男吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.22,0:01:23.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}再怎么喊也不会有人来救你的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.44,0:01:34.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.07,0:01:36.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}我果然要停下…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.40,0:01:37.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}别停啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.74,0:01:39.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}没时间解释了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.16,0:01:41.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}照我说的开车
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.20,0:01:44.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}快点 回答呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.58,0:01:46.00,Default - up,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}好…好的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.41,0:01:47.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}那…那个
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.00,0:01:49.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}北条呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.83,0:01:52.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}我不知道哪个是北条…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.38,0:01:54.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}但所有人都死了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.34,0:01:56.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}好了 快开车
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.72,0:01:58.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}如果你不想和他们一起死的话
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.18,0:01:59.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}还有…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.14,0:02:03.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}你最好别看帘子后面
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.24,0:02:20.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}真是
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.49,0:02:22.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}又不能开车
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.03,0:02:23.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}还呕吐
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.99,0:02:25.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}真是个派不上用场的家伙啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.33,0:02:27.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}喂
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.04,0:02:29.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}别想着逃跑啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.58,0:02:32.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}祠堂先生 我是瞳
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.42,0:02:33.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}是 我到了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.46,0:02:35.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}遇到了点麻烦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.42,0:02:38.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}是 那个混蛋也在
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.46,0:02:38.22,Default - up,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}这…这里是
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.76,0:02:44.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}这…这是什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.39,0:02:46.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}是…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.64,0:02:48.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}把这个混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.23,0:02:52.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}去哪了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.44,0:02:57.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}到底是怎么回事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.61,0:02:59.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}为什么会变成这样
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.65,0:03:02.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}我想回去
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.24,0:03:05.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}这是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.70,0:03:07.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}只有这里像场地一样
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.20,0:03:09.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}这是摔跤台
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.58,0:03:14.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}这是某个财阀的私有土地
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.50,0:03:17.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}聚集着无处可去的东西的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.05,0:03:20.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}大型垃圾啊尸体之类的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.80,0:03:23.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}还有我们这样的人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.51,0:03:24.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.01,0:03:28.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}请…请…请救救我
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.19,0:03:32.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}我完全不知道发生了什么
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.77,0:03:34.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}女高中生在车里…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.36,0:03:36.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}把朋友大卸八块堆成了血海
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.61,0:03:39.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}我明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.15,0:03:43.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}那恐怕是兽人干的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.03,0:03:47.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}诶 兽人…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.62,0:03:51.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}同时具备人类的大脑和野兽的牙齿
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.25,0:03:56.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}拥有远远凌驾于人类之上的力量的新人类
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.04,0:03:58.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}那就是兽人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.09,0:04:03.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}不 现在不是说这种蠢话的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.39,0:04:05.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}蠢?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.39,0:04:09.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}你刚刚说了蠢这个字吗…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.77,0:04:19.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}区区一个没有力量又矮小的人类
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.07,0:04:25.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}竟敢对着百兽之王的兽斗士狮子说蠢这个字
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.41,0:04:28.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}你是不想活了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.29,0:04:32.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}怪…怪物
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.29,0:04:34.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}给我掂掂自己的斤两
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.63,0:04:44.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}我是想帮你处理掉垃圾啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.51,0:04:47.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}他还有用处
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.60,0:04:49.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}听祠堂说
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.22,0:04:51.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}你和我之间的赌率是100比0
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.39,0:04:55.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}照这样下去的话「牙斗」就无法成立
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.27,0:04:58.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}牙…斗?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.36,0:05:00.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}的确是那样
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.15,0:05:05.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}身经百战的我和今天才第一次战斗的你之间的胜负…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.78,0:05:06.95,Default - up,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}所以就让这家伙下赌注
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.78,0:05:09.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}赌1000万我赢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.12,0:05:12.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}这样赌率就变成99比1
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.04,0:05:15.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}那家伙付的出来吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.08,0:05:16.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}让他用身体付就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.92,0:05:17.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}什么
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.79,0:05:20.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}脊髓 内脏 眼球
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.50,0:05:23.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}他还很年轻所以能卖得很贵
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.26,0:05:24.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}你别擅自…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.80,0:05:26.72,Default - up,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}我回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.47,0:05:29.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}你觉得你还逃得掉吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.64,0:05:31.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}请放开我
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.56,0:05:32.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.97,0:05:34.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}你个变态
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.85,0:05:38.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}光是我现在没马上杀掉你这一点你就该心存感激了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.36,0:05:41.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}那…那个
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.69,0:05:43.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}这到底是怎么一回事
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.82,0:05:45.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}请告诉我
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.32,0:05:47.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}话说
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.78,0:05:49.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}「牙斗」到底是…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.07,0:05:51.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}简单来说
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.41,0:05:55.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}现在开始我在这和那家伙打一场
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.45,0:05:57.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}我赢了的话你就会得救
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.12,0:06:00.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}我输了的话你就会死
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.88,0:06:03.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}死 但…但是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.09,0:06:04.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}对手是那样的怪物
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.84,0:06:06.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}你一个女孩子…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.68,0:06:14.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}与性别和体格的差距无关
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.60,0:06:17.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}獠牙更锋利者获胜
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.64,0:06:19.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}这就是「牙斗」
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,OP
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.82,0:07:54.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur8\pos(621.333,468.733)\fad(300,0)}第一牙 獠牙更锋利者获胜
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.16,0:08:02.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}这个女孩也是怪物吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.42,0:08:07.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}听说你还从未输过
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.17,0:08:10.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}王中之王
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.42,0:08:12.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}真是夸张的绰号呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.09,0:08:14.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}居然在挑衅他
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.80,0:08:16.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}是有打倒那家伙的自信吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.97,0:08:20.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}我也想要个那样的称号呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.98,0:08:23.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}你觉得「雷欧杀手」怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.81,0:08:25.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}反正最后赢的人是我
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.65,0:08:33.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}即便对手只是一只小白兔
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.36,0:08:34.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}也要用尽全力
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.03,0:08:37.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}这就是我雷欧的战斗方式
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.36,0:09:15.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}不好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.28,0:09:16.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}这女孩要被杀了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.45,0:09:18.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}我得快点去求救
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.30,0:09:37.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}这…这是怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.64,0:09:39.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}我的身体居然动不了
Comment: 0,0:09:42.77,0:09:44.81,Default,,0,0,0,,（狮子咆哮）
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.31,0:09:44.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}「雷欧狮吼」
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.27,0:09:48.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}狮子的咆哮声在猫科动物中是最大的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.69,0:09:50.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}能够威慑所有动物
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.23,0:09:52.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}使它们动弹不得
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.61,0:09:54.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}胆敢挑战王的愚蠢与恐惧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.82,0:09:57.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}就由你的身体好好记住吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.49,0:10:02.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}你这家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.20,0:10:05.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}在我雷欧狮吼之下
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.83,0:10:08.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}你应该会因为本能的恐惧不能动弹…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.25,0:10:12.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}恐惧？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.75,0:10:14.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}恐惧啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.76,0:10:16.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}从我出生开始
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.63,0:10:20.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}我的字典里就没有恐惧两个字
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.30,0:10:23.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}所有的动物都会恐惧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.81,0:10:25.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}你究竟是何方神圣
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.02,0:10:26.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}报上名来
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.81,0:10:28.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}蜜獾
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.44,0:10:31.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}兽斗士 蜜獾
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,兽斗士蜜獾
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,宇崎瞳
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.82,0:10:34.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}蜜獾
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.32,0:10:38.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}野性和暴力的化身
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.78,0:10:42.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}面对狮子等大型动物
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.37,0:10:44.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}蜜獾也会毫不畏惧地与其战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.45,0:10:47.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}被认为是世界上最强悍不怕死的生物
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.08,0:10:49.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}收入吉尼斯世界纪录
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.71,0:10:54.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}换言之蜜獾是世界小型哺乳动物的最强者
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.92,0:10:58.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}至少给我记住对手的名字吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.63,0:10:59.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}蠢货
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.43,0:11:01.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}蠢货？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.14,0:11:04.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}居然对我说这种话
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.56,0:11:06.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}你这小崽子
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.39,0:11:08.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}给我把话收回去
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.28,0:11:19.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}「蜜獾斩」
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,蜜獾斩
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.34,0:11:36.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}雷欧竟然是输了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.05,0:11:36.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}怎么可能
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.75,0:11:38.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}胜率可是99比1啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.01,0:11:40.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}到底是怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.59,0:11:42.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}难以置信
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.64,0:11:45.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}您看到了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.01,0:11:48.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}这就是我的最高杰作
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.10,0:11:50.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}兽斗士 蜜獾
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.48,0:11:56.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}被你摆了一手了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.40,0:11:59.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}一个人赢得了全部
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.49,0:12:02.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}蜜獾啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.20,0:12:09.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}真是个是挺有趣的小姑娘呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.44,0:12:38.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}如你所愿杀了你…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.23,0:12:41.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}你这个强奸犯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.99,0:12:46.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}是梦啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.20,0:12:50.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}全部都是梦啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.59,0:13:00.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}你好吵
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.30,0:13:04.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}别在我耳边大喊大叫
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.63,0:13:05.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}小心我杀了你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.85,0:13:10.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}原来不是梦啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.06,0:13:19.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}那么 完事了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.24,0:13:29.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}得救了！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.53,0:13:31.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}你搞什么
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.87,0:13:32.45,Default - up,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}太谢谢你了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.70,0:13:33.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}放开我 杀了你喂
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.83,0:13:35.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}你看你伤得这么重
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.37,0:13:36.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}哈？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.42,0:13:37.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}赶快去治疗吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.83,0:13:39.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}要是留下伤疤的话就糟了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.79,0:13:42.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}这个时间不知道还有医院开门吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.17,0:13:44.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}话说我们究竟在哪儿啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.34,0:13:45.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}我没事
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.30,0:13:47.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}这点伤一会就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.88,0:13:47.84,Default - up,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}那可不行
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.84,0:13:49.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}你可是女孩啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.65,0:13:59.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}祠堂先生?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.73,0:14:00.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.31,0:14:01.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}还 还没有
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.44,0:14:02.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}我马上就把他处理掉
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.11,0:14:07.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}啊? 这家伙吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.66,0:14:14.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}之后不知为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.95,0:14:16.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}我把她带到我的房间
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.46,0:14:19.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}说自己的伤不能去一般的医院
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.08,0:14:23.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}只是简单包扎之后就睡下了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.92,0:14:24.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.59,0:14:29.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}昨天真是非常感谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.47,0:14:32.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}那件事我不会对任何人说的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.64,0:14:33.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}所以差不多…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.14,0:14:36.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}不用你说我也会走的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.93,0:14:39.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}但是在此之前…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.90,0:14:46.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}真不错啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.15,0:14:47.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}你加得太多了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.53,0:14:50.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}我差不多该去大学了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.70,0:14:51.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}给我安静
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.32,0:14:52.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}把嘴闭上
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.03,0:14:53.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}不准呼吸
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.62,0:15:00.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}好好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.29,0:15:03.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}真可爱
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.25,0:15:07.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}这样看简直就像普通的女孩一样
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.18,0:15:17.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}昨天真是非常抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.68,0:15:19.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}不用啦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.44,0:15:20.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}硬要说的话
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.39,0:15:21.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}也是我…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.10,0:15:22.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}你不用道歉
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.23,0:15:26.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}你已经做得很棒了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.07,0:15:28.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}难道不是吗 瞳
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.32,0:15:33.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}但是比试前出了那种差错
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.70,0:15:35.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}本打算一击击倒雷欧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.45,0:15:36.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}结果却拖到中盘
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.62,0:15:39.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}害得祠堂先生为我担心了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.17,0:15:43.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}我相信你
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.04,0:15:46.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}从未感受到不安
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.30,0:15:48.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}这个人是谁
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.88,0:15:52.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}话说这又是哪位
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.05,0:15:55.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}祠堂先生
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.85,0:16:02.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}初次见面 我是祠堂零一 是瞳的监护人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.15,0:16:06.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}监护人 看起来不像是父亲啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.94,0:16:08.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}初次见面 我是….
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.23,0:16:09.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}野本裕也
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.65,0:16:14.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}高丽川大学经济学院经济专业大二学生
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.57,0:16:17.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}学号E4291
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.58,0:16:21.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}籍贯长野 现居住于大学附近的公寓里
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.46,0:16:24.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}柳泽公寓201房间
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.00,0:16:26.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}被摸根摸底的调查了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.50,0:16:28.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}说起来你觉得怎样呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.92,0:16:29.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.88,0:16:32.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}在特等席上观看「牙斗」的感想
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.18,0:16:36.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}就是…昨天的那个
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.22,0:16:39.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}没错 兽人之间的决斗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.56,0:16:41.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}兽人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.10,0:16:48.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}通过最新的基因强化手术 获得野兽能力的人们
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.73,0:16:52.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}外形和常人没什么区别
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.82,0:16:56.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}但兽化之后就这会变异进入战斗形态
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.99,0:17:01.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}怎么会… 有这种事
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.75,0:17:04.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}你对财阀有所了解吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.75,0:17:08.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}延续400年 世界上最古老的富商一族
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.13,0:17:10.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}这就是财阀
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.09,0:17:13.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}虽然在战后被解体了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.84,0:17:15.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}而当今日本的经济
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.72,0:17:19.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}八菱 三门 石田 角供
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.10,0:17:22.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}也正处于这四个财阀的支配之下
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.10,0:17:25.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}财阀们赌上各自的发言权
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.10,0:17:26.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}进行非公开的代理战争
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.48,0:17:29.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}这就是「牙斗」
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.73,0:17:33.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}每个时代被称之为最强的人们互相残杀
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.19,0:17:38.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}而近年 「牙斗」的战斗者全部都换成了兽人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.95,0:17:45.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}我们管理局的工作就是为了使「牙斗」更加顺利的进行
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.87,0:17:47.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}关于昨晚你朋友们的事
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.17,0:17:51.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}我们已经视作交通事故死处理了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.55,0:17:58.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}对…对不起 我真的不知道目的会是性侵犯
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.34,0:18:01.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}我和北条他们只不过是以前打短工时认识的而已
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.56,0:18:04.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}他们突然联系我 说要去搭讪 叫我来当司机
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.27,0:18:07.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}你小子 少在这里装蒜
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.06,0:18:09.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}在驾驶室里一脸想干的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.06,0:18:09.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}才没有
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.94,0:18:10.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}骗人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.81,0:18:12.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}我本想阻止他们的 请相信我
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.86,0:18:14.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}鬼才信你
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.32,0:18:18.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}这样的话 我也能安心的把瞳交给你了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.53,0:18:19.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}诶
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.74,0:18:21.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}让瞳来做你的贴身保镖
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.03,0:18:22.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}诶诶
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.70,0:18:25.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}才不要呢 为什么我要保护这种家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.62,0:18:29.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}他现在是 兽斗士中唯一的出资者
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.13,0:18:35.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}要是他发生了什么闪失 你也会失去「牙斗」的参赛资格
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.51,0:18:37.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}变成这样的话 我方也会损失巨大
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.68,0:18:39.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}希望你能协助我
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.05,0:18:41.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}好的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.01,0:18:44.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}如果能帮上祠堂先生的忙的话
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.02,0:18:46.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}拜托你了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.98,0:18:50.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}野本 也请你在下一场的比赛中出资
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.90,0:18:51.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}费用方面 请收下这个
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.02,0:18:54.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}这是这次分红的一部分
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.53,0:18:57.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}再见了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.74,0:19:00.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}具体的时间 之后会再给出指示的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.41,0:19:06.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}真是意外呢 社长
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.70,0:19:09.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}竟然真是个普通学生
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.37,0:19:13.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}但是既然这样 我们来管理那笔钱
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.71,0:19:16.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}把他拘束起来不更好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.38,0:19:18.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}没必要让瞳去保护他…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.30,0:19:19.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}这是必要的环节
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.97,0:19:27.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}说不定那样的年轻人 意外的能补充瞳所欠缺的部分
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.81,0:19:31.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}不管怎么说 下次的「牙斗」会是一场血雨腥风
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.52,0:19:37.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}9998 9999
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.03,0:19:40.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}果然有一亿元
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.53,0:19:45.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}你数多少次都不会变的 真是闲呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.49,0:19:46.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}是这样没错
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.99,0:19:49.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}你也差不多该去学校了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.12,0:19:53.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}不 拿着这么大笔钱才不去呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.25,0:19:55.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}话说你不也是高中生吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.88,0:19:57.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}暂时休学中
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.00,0:20:01.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}而且不知道是托谁的福 制服都成碎片了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.51,0:20:03.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.14,0:20:08.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\bord0\fn方正喵鸣\c&H00545757\fs30\b1\frz351.7\pos(470.4,530.6)}内衣 \N牙刷 \N杯子\N
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.14,0:20:08.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\bord0\fn方正喵鸣\c&H00545757\fs30\b1\pos(404.8,549.8)}水
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.14,0:20:08.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\bord0\fn方正喵鸣\c&H00545757\fs30\b1\pos(406.4,612.2)}漫画杂志HEROS
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.14,0:20:08.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\bord0\fn方正喵鸣\c&H00545757\fs30\b1\frz353.8\pos(313.6,653.8)}赶紧去
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.01,0:20:04.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}这个
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.72,0:20:05.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.43,0:20:08.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}你马上去买回来 还有甜品
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.27,0:20:11.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}你自己去买怎样呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.27,0:20:13.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}杀了你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.60,0:20:14.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}抱…抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.86,0:20:16.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}快去 跑起来
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.44,0:20:17.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}好！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.32,0:20:27.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}啊 真伤脑筋 被卷进这么麻烦的事里
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.95,0:20:33.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}不过仔细想想 这不是在和女子高中生同居吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.58,0:20:35.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.34,0:20:43.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}不好意思 稍微有东西想让你看一下
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.76,0:20:45.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}好…好
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.93,0:20:49.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}就…就是这个
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.26,0:20:52.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}诶 等等 那个
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.85,0:20:56.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}更近一点 请靠近好好看
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.31,0:20:57.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}好…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.73,0:20:59.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.91,0:21:08.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}这…这是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.75,0:21:15.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}既然让你看见了 就不能简单放你回去
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.09,0:21:21.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}把你知道关于蜜獾的事全部说出来
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.93,0:21:29.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}关于我的事 来问我怎样
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.81,0:21:32.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}我正好就在这附近呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.18,0:21:35.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}蜜獾
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.27,0:21:36.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}瞳
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.86,0:21:45.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}来 开始吧 「牙斗」
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,ED
Comment: 0,0:23:16.16,0:23:17.95,Default,,0,0,0,,第一集 指引我吧 小押绘
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.16,0:23:17.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}指引我吧 小押绘
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.25,0:23:21.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}明明听说家店的热香饼很好吃才来的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.08,0:23:23.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}这些客人都是什么人啊 我都不好意思进去
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.92,0:23:24.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}碍事
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.88,0:23:29.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}砂糖热香饼蜂蜜特别版两个
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.55,0:23:32.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}这个人 连我的份都…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.76,0:23:36.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}蜜獾 以及黑喉响蜜鴷
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.39,0:23:39.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}通过最喜欢的蜂蜜 维持着共生关系
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.18,0:23:42.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}这两只动物的相遇 是必然
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.98,0:23:46.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}话说 你是谁
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.73,0:23:51.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}不过 小押绘才不是什么兽人
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.24,0:23:54.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}定期报告
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.32,0:23:56.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}对于把王者狮子打倒的蜜獾
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.20,0:23:58.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}各个财阀都围绕她开始谋划策略
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.16,0:24:00.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}假如 目标瞄准的是野本的话
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.08,0:24:03.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}无法预测瞳是否会去保护他
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.04,0:24:07.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur8\pos(621.333,468.733)\fad(00,0)}第二牙 糟糕 要迷上了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.96,0:24:06.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}下一集「糟糕 要迷上了」 以上
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.03,0:06:32.74,op-jp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur8}混ざり合う叫びは静寂を切り裂く
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.95,0:06:35.54,op-jp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur8}研ぎ澄ませる野生で
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.62,0:06:38.37,op-jp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur8}勝者だけが繋ぐ明日
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.37,0:06:41.21,op-jp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur8}鋭く磨いた牙
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.29,0:06:44.00,op-jp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur8}噛み付くその狂気
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.04,0:06:48.17,op-jp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur8}立ち向かおうか？戦いにわけなどいらない
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.17,0:06:51.05,op-jp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur8}強さ求めるだけ
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.85,0:07:06.36,op-jp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur8}螺旋に繋がれた生命の約束
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.57,0:07:11.99,op-jp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur8}止まらない進化が呼び覚ましてく　命の鼓動
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.99,0:07:17.20,op-jp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur8}狂おしく飢えて　乾いた心だけ
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.20,0:07:25.17,op-jp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur8}溢れる狂気も纏って　今立ち上がる
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.17,0:07:25.92,op-jp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur8}Shout and roar！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.92,0:07:31.13,op-jp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur8}解き放つ咆哮　その闇を震わす
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.18,0:07:33.93,op-jp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur8}恐れなく踏み出した
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.93,0:07:36.64,op-jp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur8}その一歩が痛みを呼ぶ
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.64,0:07:39.52,op-jp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur8}鋭く刺さる罪は
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.52,0:07:42.31,op-jp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur8}この世界に潜む
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.31,0:07:46.48,op-jp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur8}真実はその嘘を飲み込んだままで
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.48,0:07:49.61,op-jp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur8}全てを見つめてる
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.03,0:06:32.74,op-cn,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur8}混杂交织的叫喊打破寂静
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.95,0:06:35.54,op-cn,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur8}敏感的野兽
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.62,0:06:38.37,op-cn,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur8}唯有胜者拥有明天
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.37,0:06:41.21,op-cn,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur8}打磨出锋利的獠牙
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.29,0:06:44.00,op-cn,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur8}紧咬不放的疯狂
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.04,0:06:48.17,op-cn,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur8}去迎敌吗？战斗不需要理由
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.17,0:06:51.05,op-cn,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur8}唯独追求强大
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.85,0:07:06.36,op-cn,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur8}螺旋维系的生命的约定
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.57,0:07:11.99,op-cn,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur8}无止境的进化唤起生命的颤动
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.99,0:07:17.20,op-cn,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur8}疯狂地渴望 只剩干枯的心
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.20,0:07:25.17,op-cn,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur8}满溢的疯狂缠身 现在站起来
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.17,0:07:25.92,op-cn,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur8}叫喊和咆哮！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.92,0:07:31.13,op-cn,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur8}被解放的咆哮 使黑暗颤抖
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.18,0:07:33.93,op-cn,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur8}无所畏惧的迈出一步
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.93,0:07:36.64,op-cn,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur8}哪怕这一步会招致疼痛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.64,0:07:39.52,op-cn,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur8}锐利地刺入的罪孽
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.52,0:07:42.31,op-cn,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur8}潜伏在这个世界之中
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.31,0:07:46.48,op-cn,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur8}真实吞咽下这份谎言
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.48,0:07:49.61,op-cn,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur8}却注视着一切
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.26,0:22:08.68,ed-jp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}欲望のままにあれ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.84,0:22:11.14,ed-jp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}どうにでもなれなんて
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.30,0:22:13.68,ed-jp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}可愛いもの見たさで
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.72,0:22:16.10,ed-jp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}近づいちゃ行けない
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.23,0:22:18.64,ed-jp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}儚げな笑顔も
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.73,0:22:21.02,ed-jp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}水色の涙も
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.15,0:22:23.52,ed-jp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}カムフラージュ切れない
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.65,0:22:26.15,ed-jp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}危ないその匂い
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.17,0:22:44.05,ed-jp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}か弱いフリの牙に
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.13,0:22:49.01,ed-jp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}噛み付かれないように
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.34,0:22:55.06,ed-jp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}あの子はどこから見ても
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.31,0:22:58.60,ed-jp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}ケダモノダモノ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.26,0:22:08.68,ed-cn,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}遵循本能的欲望
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.84,0:22:11.14,ed-cn,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}变成怎样都无所谓
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.30,0:22:13.68,ed-cn,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}对可爱事物充满好奇
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.72,0:22:16.10,ed-cn,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}但却不可以靠近
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.23,0:22:18.64,ed-cn,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}无论是梦幻的笑容
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.73,0:22:21.02,ed-cn,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}还是淡蓝色的眼泪
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.15,0:22:23.52,ed-cn,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}都无法掩盖
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.65,0:22:26.15,ed-cn,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}这危险的气息
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.17,0:22:44.05,ed-cn,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}要当心别被
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.13,0:22:49.01,ed-cn,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}这看似弱小的獠牙紧咬
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.34,0:22:55.06,ed-cn,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}不论从哪个角度看
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.31,0:22:58.60,ed-cn,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}那个孩子都是鄙劣的野兽
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,
